---
/**
 * ai-agents/0001 · Figure 8 — Level 7, Workflow vs Agent
 * (a fixed linear chain you write vs a model-driven loop).
 * Verbatim from source; shared <marker>s inlined + namespaced (-f8). See Fig1.
 */
---

<figure>
    <svg
        viewBox="0 0 560 170"
        role="img"
        aria-label="Workflow is a fixed linear chain you write; agent is a model-driven loop"
    >
        <defs>
            <marker
                id="arw-f8"
                viewBox="0 0 10 10"
                refX="8.5"
                refY="5"
                markerWidth="7"
                markerHeight="7"
                orient="auto-start-reverse"
            >
                <path d="M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 z" fill="#6b675f"></path>
            </marker>
            <marker
                id="arwA-f8"
                viewBox="0 0 10 10"
                refX="8.5"
                refY="5"
                markerWidth="7"
                markerHeight="7"
                orient="auto-start-reverse"
            >
                <path d="M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 z" fill="#7a1f12"></path>
            </marker>
        </defs>
        <g font-family="ui-sans-serif,system-ui,sans-serif">
            <text
                x="140"
                y="22"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="12"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#1f3a5a">WORKFLOW — you write the path</text
            >
            <rect x="14" y="56" width="72" height="36" rx="7" fill="#fff" stroke="#1f3a5a"
            ></rect><text x="50" y="79" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11">step 1</text>
            <rect x="104" y="56" width="72" height="36" rx="7" fill="#fff" stroke="#1f3a5a"
            ></rect><text x="140" y="79" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11">step 2</text>
            <rect x="194" y="56" width="72" height="36" rx="7" fill="#fff" stroke="#1f3a5a"
            ></rect><text x="230" y="79" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11">step 3</text>
            <line x1="86" y1="74" x2="102" y2="74" stroke="#6b675f" marker-end="url(#arw-f8)"
            ></line>
            <line x1="176" y1="74" x2="192" y2="74" stroke="#6b675f" marker-end="url(#arw-f8)"
            ></line>
            <text x="140" y="120" text-anchor="middle" font-size="10.5" fill="#2f5d3a"
                >predictable · cheap · testable</text
            >
            <line x1="288" y1="10" x2="288" y2="150" stroke="#d8d4c8" stroke-dasharray="4 4"></line>
            <text
                x="430"
                y="22"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="12"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#7a1f12">AGENT — the model writes the path</text
            >
            <rect x="360" y="48" width="140" height="42" rx="9" fill="#f1eee2" stroke="#7a1f12"
            ></rect><text
                x="430"
                y="74"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="11"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#7a1f12">LLM decides next step</text
            >
            <rect x="396" y="118" width="68" height="30" rx="7" fill="#fff" stroke="#d8d4c8"
            ></rect><text x="430" y="138" text-anchor="middle" font-size="10">tool</text>
            <path d="M 415 90 L 415 116" stroke="#6b675f" marker-end="url(#arw-f8)"></path>
            <path
                d="M 452 116 C 470 96, 470 96, 455 92"
                fill="none"
                stroke="#7a1f12"
                marker-end="url(#arwA-f8)"></path>
            <text x="505" y="112" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9.5" fill="#7a1f12">loop</text>
        </g>
    </svg>
    <figcaption>
        Workflow = the <code>if/else</code> you wrote · Agent = the <code>if/else</code> the model writes
        at runtime.
    </figcaption>
</figure>
